dct_description_sm: Some tourist sites are shown pictorially. Inset map: Attiki (scale 1:700,000). Index on recto includes tourist sites; trolley bus and bus services, including "Pireefs and Athine suburbs bus terminals" and "Provincial bus stations." Verso includes tourist information, site descriptions, history, images. North oriented towards upper right on map. "No 18--April 1971." Alternate title: Greece Athine. Includes tourist information and transportation. Relief shown pictorally. Verso: tourist information and site descriptions. North Decimal Degree 37.996389. South Decimal Degree 37.958333. West Decimal Degree 23.708333. East Decimal Degree 23.760556. National Tourist Organisation of Greece-Athine.
